{%- comment -%} DUK/FAQ empty state — shown by main-duk when no FAQ (`group` / `accordion_item`) blocks are configured. Add blocks in the theme editor to replace it. {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="faq-empty">
  <p class="faq-empty__title">{{ 'faq.empty_title' | t }}</p>
  <p class="faq-empty__text">{{ 'faq.empty_text' | t }}</p>
</div>
